GetLatestMarketData(InstrumentKey)

Returns latest known market data for specified instrument Pay attention, that returned value may be empty. Some data providers demand to subscribe to instrument events first. If no any subscribers for specified instrument, then empty data will be returned

Subscribes multiple handlers to market quotes of specified instruments

Parameters

subscriptionInfos SubscriptionInfo[]

Remarks

Consider using CreateSubscriber(IMarketDataProvider, InstrumentKey, SubscriptionModel, MarketDataEventHandler) to create IMarketDataSubscriber. This object supports IDisposable for automatic unsubscription Also, for multiple subscriptions, consider using CreateBatchSubscription(IMarketDataProvider)

Unsubscribe(params MarketDataSubscriptionKey[])

Unsubscribes specified subscriptionKeys

void Unsubscribe(params MarketDataSubscriptionKey[] subscriptionKeys)

Parameters

subscriptionKeys MarketDataSubscriptionKey[]

A collection of subscription keys

Remarks

Since the provider implementation may have optimization for multiple unsubscriptions, it is better to call this method for the whole group of keys instead of calling Unsubscribe(params MarketDataSubscriptionKey[]) for each subscription key
